{"tid":1531964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大會指警方賤招向市民記者灑螢光粉 防暴警舉紅旗射胡椒水劑","createTime":"2019-09-02T11:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:17:51.000Z","uid":17646,"like":172,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"c4bcb92b8ed6b84893250973646fb2820d726a2a","tid":1531964,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190902/large/1567421954_9c2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190902%2Flarge%2F1567421954_9c2f.jpg&h=33e7612e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190902/large/1567423379_2cf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190902%2Flarge%2F1567423379_2cf6.jpg&h=2cb3f970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金鐘添馬公園下午舉行「全民三罷」集會，警方於特首辦外設置水馬陣，阻止今日集會的市民靠近。至傍晚時份，逾百名市民移師至特首辦門外聚集，其間有人用雷射筆照射特首辦，又向特首辦外的防暴警叫囂，多名手持盾牌的防暴警要求市民立即離開，又舉起紅旗示意市民停止衝擊，未幾有警員向市民多次發射胡椒水劑，現場一片混亂。<br />\n<br />\n據知，大會傍晚宣佈有直升機經過金鐘添馬公園的上空，然後向人群灑螢光粉，由於當時雨勢頗大，市民全部舉起雨傘避雨，並不知情，其後《蘋果》用紫外光照射在場市民的衣服，發現每人的上衣及褲都佈滿螢光粉。"},{"pid":"61462d66258b3c16989f35d84f5310010ad24cd9","tid":1531964,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df98607e52f78214ba74c0bc18ea070847fb139c","tid":1531964,"uid":58781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"a061f55d22fd24de6221a99d12b7861c09fee179","tid":1531964,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa991c6b0cf44a3b20b455b3e3571872c7712ede","tid":1531964,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src