n金鐘添馬公園下午舉行「全民三罷」集會，警方於特首辦外設置水馬陣，阻止今日集會的市民靠近。至傍晚時份，逾百名市民移師至特首辦門外聚集，其間有人用雷射筆照射特首辦，又向特首辦外的防暴警叫囂，多名手持盾牌的防暴警要求市民立即離開，又舉起紅旗示意市民停止衝擊，未幾有警員向市民多次發射胡椒水劑，現場一片混亂。<br />\n<br />\n據知，大會傍晚宣佈有直升機經過金鐘添馬公園的上空，然後向人群灑螢光粉，由於當時雨勢頗大，市民全部舉起雨傘避雨，並不知情，其後《蘋果》用紫外光照射在場市民的衣服，發現每人的上衣及褲都佈滿螢光粉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:23:12.000Z","msg":"用潤滑油抹（例如WD40)"},{"pid":"10fa48feecb2ea2ca3048a36ffe7e731974690cf","tid":1531964,"uid":18296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:24:06.000Z","msg":"uv燈唔係個個有，有冇簡單方法街邊都check到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d26edca7067ebb03377695b2384613404801e8c","tid":1531964,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52f29c1aa5852553967bffcc27912bd80c8ff0d5","tid":1531964,"uid":15362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"18281e14362ab70271405f2cc42392881c8a48e4","tid":1531964,"uid":79410,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好去鴨記買D 幾舊水搖控飛機. <br />\n千祈千祈唔好向住直昇機撞過去."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"十幾架飛過去同佢攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"十幾架. 都係皮幾嘢. <br />\n皮幾嘢KO 機師, 黑狗條命. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf3f83a4a312ceee630323184dbd7137d1c7cf1","tid":1531964,"uid":2036,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c4bcb92b8ed6b84893250973646fb2820d726a2a","tid":1531964,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190902/large/1567421954_9c2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190902%2Flarge%2F1567421954_9c2f.jpg&h=33e7612e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190902/large/1567423379_2cf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: